text: John Le Marchant may refer to: *John Le Marchant (British Army officer, born 1766) (1766–1812), British Army cavalry major-general killed at Salamanca *Sir John Le Marchant (British Army officer, born 1803) (1803–1874), British Army general and Governor of Newfoundland, son of the above ==See also== *John Marchant (disambiguation)
title: John Le Marchant
